    <subfield code="y">00000 Definition of the Adler Angles  at the nucleon (true) level (a) and the nuclear level (b). The momenta of the particles are defined in the $\vec q  = \vec p_{\nu}-\vec p_{\mu}$ rest frame.</subfield>
